data.meta_description: tibet coins - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document discusses several Thai gold coins issued between BE2523-BE2543 (1980-2000). It notes that the coins commemorate anniversaries of the king, as well as other occasions. It also mentions that during World War 2, Thailand issued occupation coins that were intended to circulate in occupied Malaya but did not.
